OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FAfter almost 1,000 years, the Bayeux
OL,8,FTapestry is back on English soil
OL,9,Ffollowing a high-security nighttime
OL,10,Fdelivery to the British Museum across
OL,11,Fthe Channel that was shrouded in
OL,12,Fsecrecy.
OL,14,FIn scenes like a heist movie in
OL,15,Freverse, the priceless Medieval
OL,16,Fartwork was taken to the museum in the
OL,17,Fdead of night, after a high-tech,
OL,18,Ftight-security operation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThe artwork is on loan from France and
OL,8,Fwill go on display from September 10
OL,9,Funtil next July.
OL,11,FAmong the most famous artworks on the
OL,12,Fplanet, the enormous tapestry records
OL,13,Fthe 1066 Norman invasion of England by
OL,14,FWilliam the Conqueror.
OL,16,F"It feels extraordinary that after so
OL,17,Fmuch work and planning and care and
OL,18,Fthought that it's actually happening,"
OL,19,FBritish Museum Director Nicholas
OL,20,FCullinan said as he awaited the
OL,21,Fartwork's arrival.
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,F"It's the first time in 1,000 years
OL,8,Fthat such an important piece of
OL,9,FBritish ` French too ` history is
OL,10,Fgoing to be on these shores," he said.
OL,11,F"It's incredibly exciting."
OL,13,FThe 70-metre tapestry was folded
OL,14,Faccordion-style in a climate-
OL,15,Fcontrolled case that was placed inside
OL,16,Fa shock-absorbing cradle. That went
OL,17,Finto a lorry that crossed from France
OL,18,Fthrough the Channel Tunnel.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@]O]sD@AOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FAfter an 11-hour, 350-mile trip,
OL,8,Fescorted by police, the lorry backed
OL,9,Fslowly into a loading bay at the
OL,10,Fmuseum, where workers gingerly eased
OL,11,Fthe container, the size of a small
OL,12,Fcar, to the ground. Museum staff and
OL,13,FBritish and French diplomats broke
OL,14,Finto applause.
OL,16,FThe priceless cargo will spend several
OL,17,Fdays acclimatising before it is
OL,18,Fcarefully unpacked and unfolded for an
OL,19,Fexhibition that the museum expects to
OL,20,Fbe one of the most popular in its
OL,21,Fhistory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FAbout 100,000 tickets were sold on
OL,8,Ftheir first day on sale this month.
OL,10,F"It was like trying to get tickets to
OL,11,FGlastonbury," Cullinan said. "I don't
OL,12,Ftake for granted that people care that
OL,13,Fmuch about a 1,000-year-old
OL,14,Fembroidery. I think that's an amazing
OL,15,Fthing."
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@MO]sD@^OUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
