PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FIn an article published in The Times
OL,8,Fon Friday, the French president said
OL,9,Fthe loan was a "tangible expression of
OL,10,Flong-standing friendship and a sign of
OL,11,Four shared desire to see France and
OL,12,Fthe United Kingdom build their future
OL,13,Ftogether".
OL,15,FHe said the two nations recognise what
OL,16,Fsets each other apart, but also "their
OL,17,Fnatural affinity and what they can
OL,18,Fachieve when they join forces".
OL,26,@qD@POUuD@IO]xD@aOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
