PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,F"This is what our partnership must
OL,8,Fcontinue to embody," he said. "The UK
OL,9,Fis a strategic partner, ally and
OL,10,Ffriend of France."
OL,12,FOn X, he posted a picture of the White
OL,13,FCliffs of Dover illuminated with the
OL,14,Fword Merci and art from the tapestry.
OL,16,FHe said, "Long live the Entente
OL,17,FCordiale," in reference to the pivotal
OL,18,Falliance signed between France and
OL,19,FEngland in 1904, which shaped both
OL,20,Fworld wars.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@TO]pD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
