PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FIn return, the British Museum will
OL,8,Floan treasures from the Sutton Hoo
OL,9,Fhoard ` artefacts from a 7th-century
OL,10,FAnglo-Saxon ship burial ` and other
OL,11,Fitems to museums in Normandy.
OL,13,FRetired British diplomat Peter
OL,14,FRicketts, who helped secure the deal
OL,15,Fas the UK's special envoy for the
OL,16,Ftapestry, said: "It's an extraordinary
OL,17,Fmark of friendship and confidence in
OL,18,Fthe UK to entrust this object to us
OL,19,Ffor a year."
OL,26,@xD@QOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
