PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,F"Macron, when he offered us the
OL,8,Ftapestry, I think he understood that
OL,9,Fit would have far more impact in the
OL,10,FUK than it does in France, because
OL,11,Fit's more fundamental to our national
OL,12,Fstory," he said. Everybody (in
OL,13,FBritain) knows 1066."
OL,15,FIt features 627 people and 737 animals
OL,16,Fand tells its story in 58 scenes
OL,17,Fbrimming with vivid and sometimes gory
OL,18,Fdetail. There are scenes of hand-to-
OL,19,Fhand combat, mutilated bodies and
OL,20,FHarold, felled by an arrow through his
OL,21,Feye.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@GO]uD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
