PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,F"It has an emotional richness that is
OL,8,Freally difficult to get from written
OL,9,Fsources," said Millie Horton-Insch,
OL,10,Fproject curator for the British Museum
OL,11,Fexhibition.
OL,13,F"It just brings people closer to this
OL,14,Fhistory than any other object can.
OL,15,FIt's not the same as reading a text.
OL,16,FYou are looking at something that was
OL,17,Fhandled by the people who lived
OL,18,Fthrough it and felt compelled to
OL,19,Frecord these events in this way. "
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]uD@AOU{D@bOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
