OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783711191
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry arrives in England
OL,4,Cafter secret overnight journey from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,F"It's not really made of any blingy
OL,8,Ffabric," she said. "It's not gold,
OL,9,Fit's not silver. There wasn't the same
OL,10,Ftemptation to cut it up and make it
OL,11,Finto vestments or repurpose it for
OL,12,Fanything."
OL,14,FSome French cultural figures opposed
OL,15,Fthe loan, arguing that moving the
OL,16,Ftapestry was too risky. Cullinan said
OL,17,Fthe expert teams went to great lengths
OL,18,Fto ensure its safety, including making
OL,19,Ftwo trial runs of the journey to show
OL,20,Fit would not cause the fragile item
OL,21,Ftoo much stress.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@HO]pD@TOUtD@JO]
